{"tid":61584,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[SoSad音樂]肥婆悲歌《誰願意與肥婆在一起》MV","createTime":"2016-12-31T10:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T13:51:21.000Z","uid":50360,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"acd7d1dc2b820273cae3216ae495ce33109d4e5c","tid":61584,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T10:43:10.000Z","msg":"肥就係罪，肥婆唔值得被愛。係依個世界，係咪只有又瘦又靚嘅女人先可以拍拖，肥婆就要送去填海？<br />\n<br />\nP.S.：2016年最後一首歌，祝各巴絲新年快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/eqa3hjwf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Feqa3hjwf&h=c83daded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《誰願意與肥婆在一起》MV：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=geJdgEEkwhI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgeJdgEEkwhI&d=kmuJDYW%2Fcb8H7CPrNV7%2FwAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=613fd457\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=geJdgEEkwhI</a>"},{"pid":"2b9181597a6df2f053049a37ef9e8998273a12dd","tid":61584,"uid":50360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T10:43:48.000Z","msg":"《誰願意與肥婆在一起》<br />\n<br />\n原曲：只要和你在一起<br />\n改編填詞：山卡啦<br />\n主唱：isaB<br />\nMV製作：山卡啦<br />\n<br />\n纏綿情侶放閃溫馨親密夜城景況  肥胖的我獨自遊蕩  <br />\n為何聖誕夜沒人伴我很心寒  傷心總扮作開朗<br />\n來照鏡  是我脂肪太多<br />\n令男生只 敢於觀看<br />\n問哪位同情   誰跟肥婆拍拖<br />\n<br />\n肥婆難說以身相許因為像男子漢<br />\n肥大臂彎不會捱餓<br />\n無奈肚腩脂肪大上圍得A貨<br />\n戀愛事猶如淨低纖瘦美人   男人追趕<br />\n一件件肥婆不可愛<br />\n恥笑我肥野  很傷我<br />\n<br />\n*肥婆脂肪兩袋  肥婆就跌落台<br />\n有冇呼吸都會墮進深海 <br />\n食野多恐龍成災  肥得會發生意外<br />\n可衝破道牆 然而釘蓋<br />\n肥婆通通有害  肥婆沒瘦下來<br />\n決意今生於美食裡淹蓋<br />\n是世界不能容  脂肪滿載<br />\n要後退  待肥脂肪不復再*<br />\n<br />\n肥婆何以惹起公開審問萬人追看<br />\n曾被抹黑本性淫蕩<br />\n肥胖惹各種死罪沒人敢反抗<br />\nByeBye肉連同象腿虎背結合  肥膏生瘡<br />\n比大象麒麟都堅壯<br />\n可會有男友   喜歡我<br />\n<br />\nRepeat * <br />\n<br />\n肥婆單身世代  為何沒有未來<br />\n滿佈脂肪戀愛沒法精彩<br />\n若這生黯然離開  肥的我再不按捺<br />\n可找個毒男齊齊戀愛<br />\n肥婆單身有害  肥婆望瘦下來<br />\n決意不想於美食裡掩蓋<br />\n是世界不能容  脂肪滿載<br />\n沒瘦下的肥人  永遠被害<br />\n就似中不瘦降  嘲笑活該<br />\n怎樣過  我人生只可食菜<br />\n<br />\n肥肉滿佈  是否不可被愛"},{"pid":"c4aa8edfe364da8c78a2e9dee26ae5ac4bfd1412","tid":61584,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T10:44:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"910d4b6701c6a48fa5e024643115e16f3256b107","tid":61584,"uid":49767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb239decf35d4744be6bbbac37daed09cb51ff0","tid":61584,"uid":2350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T11:32:46.000Z","msg":"點解成日肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c48b11b1886f13ddf7b1b50b71f437b20366df","tid":61584,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T11:54:51.000Z","msg":"食菜係唔會瘦架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb349489cf157236bbe5cc8831c05284bcce7adf","tid":61584,"uid":66909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"啦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465de175054a627490e60a4baf404ac38149005f","tid":61584,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}